#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:4
msgid "简介：用于比较两个张量的元素, 与`!=`等价。"
msgstr "Introduction: Used to compare elements of two tensors, equivalent to `!=`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:6
msgid "作为`tensor`的内置运算符使用, 如`x!=y`。"
msgstr "Used as a built-in operator for `tensor`, such as `x!=y`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | :---: |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | 张量数据, 左操作数, 代表要进行比较的主数据 |\n"
"| `other`   | `tensor` | 张量数据, 右操作数, 与`input`逐元素进行比较 |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | :---: |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | Tensor data, left operand, representing the primary data to be compared |\n"
"| `other` | `tensor` | Tensor data, right operand, compared element-wise with `input` |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：同`input`的shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: A tensor with the same shape as `input`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

