#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:38
msgid "以下示例实现了对张量`x0`、`x1`做`!=`运算："
msgstr "The following example implements the `!=` operation on tensors `x0` and `x1`:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Comparing_Ops/ne.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_ne(in_ptr0, in_ptr1, out_ptr0, N: tl.constexpr, XBLOCK: tl.constexpr, XBLOCK_SUB: tl.constexpr):\n"
"       offset = tl.program_id(0) * XBLOCK\n"
"       base1 = tl.arange(0, XBLOCK_SUB)\n"
"       loops1: tl.constexpr = XBLOCK // XBLOCK_SUB\n"
"       for loop1 in range(loops1):\n"
"           x_index = offset + (loop1 * XBLOCK_SUB) + base1\n"
"           tmp0 = tl.load(in_ptr0 + x_index, mask=x_index < N)\n"
"           tmp1 = tl.load(in_ptr1 + x_index, mask=x_index < N)\n"
"           tmp2 = tmp0 != tmp1\n"
"           tl.store(out_ptr0 + x_index, tmp2, mask=x_index < N)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

